# Copy this file to .env (or .env.local) and fill in the values.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser.
#
# No VITE_ variables are required.
#
# Maps/routing use HERE exclusively, and the HERE API key lives SERVER-SIDE only
# (server/.env → HERE_API_KEY). The browser map fetches the key at runtime from
# the auth-gated /api/here/config endpoint, so there is intentionally no
# VITE_HERE_* var here and the key is never baked into the frontend bundle.
